    intro: 'Jimi Hendrix transformed the electric guitar from a musical instrument into a force of nature. In just four years of major recordings, he expanded the vocabulary of rock guitar with feedback, distortion, and wah-wah effects that no one had imagined possible. He remains the standard against which all rock guitarists are measured.',
